ActFirearms Act
SubjectContribution Agreements federal - provincial
PrecisOrder renewing the authority of the Minister of Public Safety and Emergency Preparedness to enter into CONTRIBUTION AGREEMENTS with the governments of the provinces who choose to administer the Firearms Act within their jurisdiction, including the reimbursement of certain expenditures incurred in its administration.
